### Special Attributes

There are some special attributes which the value must be set as array:

Name | Value
---- | -----
`class[]` | Contains array of HTML class names.
`data[]` | Contains array of HTML5 `data-*` name as the array key and its value.
`style[]` | Contains array of CSS property as the array key and its value.

**Example:**

~~~ .php
echo HTML::span("", [
    'class[]' => ['color', 'black'],
    'style[]' => [
        'background-color' => '#000'
    ],
    'data[]' => [
        'key' => 'offset',
        'value' => 0
    ]
]);
~~~